{
  "stem": "18778.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 352.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew I was loved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I enjoyed being wherever children were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our town was actually also the birthplace of Joseph Goebbels, who became the propaganda minister in the Hitler regime.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our town, everybody knew everybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody knew my father, first of all, because he was-- had a well-known law firm, I would say probably one of the most successful, perhaps raising envy on the part of some colleagues, especially non-Jewish colleagues.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And life was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We lived in a big house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had-- I went to a Jewish day school, so that I did not suffer some of the early anti-Semitic situations that other children experienced who did not go to Jewish day schools and who were eventually thrown out of their schools.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and my playmates, naturally, were also from school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And with the exception of neighborhood children, who started to call me all kinds of names when I was four, five years old, I didn't really have too many negative experiences as a child.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, approximately 70,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very close to the next town, which was Monchengladbach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Today that's all one municipality.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time, these were separate towns with separate Jewish congregations and separate synagogues and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But for instance, there was a Jewish athletic club that I belonged to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would travel once a week to Monchengladbach to-- to do athletic activities and meet other Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a Jewish community center there where that took place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it was a close-knit community, Jewish community specifically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my father had also in the beginning many non-Jewish clients.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was well known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, he was a known Social Democrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure what these activities entailed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
